00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:23.240
today we are talking about Xiphophorus Maculatus

00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:25.200
commonly called Platy fish

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:29.240
Is a fresh water fish from the Poeciliidae family

00:00:29.240 --> 00:00:32.800
and is widespread in the Central America

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:34.880
from Belise and Mexico

00:00:35.380 --> 00:00:42.540
The colors in nature that usually are a little off

00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:48.980
but in breeding are very alive tones

00:00:50.420 --> 00:00:54.778
the most popular species are the coral, Red, Sunburst, Dawn,

00:00:54.778 --> 00:00:59.998
Crescent (mikey mouse), Gold, High fin, Blue spot,

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:06.980
Tiger, Red / Silver Wag, Tuxedo and many others

00:01:18.671 --> 00:01:25.231
Platy fish is a very lively fish but also very peaceful

00:01:25.240 --> 00:01:29.820
and live well in the community

00:01:31.260 --> 00:01:36.980
generally it is a fish with small size

00:01:36.980 --> 00:01:42.220
and compressed on the sides

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:52.960
prominent flukes and dorsal fin

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:02.420
big eye and large mouth

00:02:02.820 --> 00:02:07.700
there is not sexual dimorphism between males and females

00:02:14.060 --> 00:02:19.340
the only thing that characterizes the male is the gonopodium

00:02:20.600 --> 00:02:26.420
(sexual organ is clearly visible near the anal fin)

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:40.000
Is an ovoviviparous animal then females after a pregnancy of 30-40 days

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:43.160
will give birth to live young fish

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:49.460
Xiphophorus Maculatus usually feeding with plant and animal material

00:02:49.460 --> 00:02:56.740
like flakes and granules or artemia napulii

